B.X5=new A.fy("Food date labels can be confusing. For most products, the date is about quality, not safety \u2014 and throwing food away on the printed date is one of the biggest drivers of household waste.")
B.WI=new A.cs("Common terms, demystified")
B.Zr=s(["Best By / Best Before \u2014 peak flavor and quality. Usually safe to eat past the date if stored properly.","Use By \u2014 last date for peak quality on perishables. A few items (like infant formula) should not be eaten past this date.","Sell By \u2014 a hint for the store's inventory. Food is typically safe days or weeks after.","Expiration Date \u2014 rare; usually reserved for items where safety really does expire (infant formula, some medications)."],t.s)
B.VJ=new A.cE(B.Zr)
B.Wp=new A.eX("\u2705","Trust your senses more than the printed date for most foods \u2014 look, smell, feel.")
B.a27=s([B.X5,B.WI,B.VJ,B.Wp],t.F)
B.Xu=new A.el("date-labels","\ud83c\udff7\ufe0f","Reading food date labels",'What "Best By", "Use By", and "Sell By" actually mean.',B.a27)
B.WY=new A.cs("Fruits and vegetables")
B.a1d=s(["Mold with fuzzy green, white, or black spots.","Slimy or mushy texture.","Strong or fermented smell.","Excessive leaking or heavy browning."],t.s)
B.Wc=new A.cE(B.a1d)
B.Xc=new A.fy("Slightly soft or wrinkled produce is usually still usable \u2014 think soups, sauces, baking.")
B.WC=new A.cs("Dairy")
B.a39=s(["Sour smell.","Curdling or separation in milk.","Mold growth on soft cheeses \u2014 discard.","Unusual flavor."],t.s)
B.VI=new A.cE(B.a39)
B.Wg=new A.eX("\ud83e\uddc0","Hard cheeses (parmesan, pecorino) are resilient: trim a small mold spot and the rest is typically fine.")
B.WU=new A.cs("Meat, poultry and seafood")
B.a3o=s(["Sticky or slimy surface.","Rotten or sulfur-like odor.","Gray, green or dull coloring."],t.s)
B.W_=new A.cE(B.a3o)
B.Wf=new A.eX("\u26a0\ufe0f","Do not taste meat or seafood to test freshness \u2014 when in doubt, throw it out.")
B.WF=new A.cs("Eggs")
B.a4t=s(["Strong or foul smell once cracked.","Float test: an egg that floats in water may be old \u2014 inspect carefully before using."],t.s)
B.VY=new A.cE(B.a4t)
